Class GridGraph

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.gridgraph.structure.GridGraph
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, AutoCloseable, org.apache.tinkerpop.gremlin.structure.Graph, org.apache.tinkerpop.gremlin.structure.util.Host
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    GridEmptyGraph, GridGraph.AnonymousGridGraph, GridResultGraph

    public class GridGraph
extends Object
implements org.apache.tinkerpop.gremlin.structure.Graph, Serializable
    GridGraph graph database implementation of the Gremlin graph interface. Use GridGraphFactory to open and configure GridGraph instances.

    guobao.chen
